The #HairMafia at it again @brandonliberati  @vickicasciola 
This look was so much fun to create on the one and only @jennyxo_x  All the details below on how we achieved this look ! ⬇️🚨
#hairtalk extensions :
Customized a 20inch #2 hairband with 25inch tape in extensions #6  #3/7cm  # 2 to create more length and dimension  for her half up half down crown braid ! 
#DesignMe product used :
Puff.me to create texture in the crown braid 
Hold.me hairspray on level 2 to create a Heat protectant barrier and soft hold . 
.
